code: public void testVersionIsCurrent() {     /* This test will only work properly in gradle because in gradle we run the tests          * using the jar. */     assertNotNull(Version.CURRENT.hash).     assertEquals(org.elasticsearch.Version.CURRENT.major, Version.CURRENT.major).     assertEquals(org.elasticsearch.Version.CURRENT.minor, Version.CURRENT.minor).     assertEquals(org.elasticsearch.Version.CURRENT.revision, Version.CURRENT.revision). }
